lore: §7The Spider is an enemy in Skyblock that naturally
§7spawns in the Spiders Den and a player's Private
§7Island. Its common drops are String and Spider
§7Eyes. There are different variants of spiders
§7that spawn in the Spider's Den, which include the
§7Dasher Spider, Splitter Spider, and Weaver Spider.
